### Register my status
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/status-reports
Content-Type: application/json
X-Member-Id: 1

{
  "announcementId": 1,
  "stage": "DOCUMENT",
  "notifiedDate": "2026-06-22",
  "notifiedTimeText": "14시대",
  "notificationChannel": "SMS",
  "result": "PASSED"
}

### Realtime home feed
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/realtime/feed?size=20

### Announcement realtime summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/realtime/announcements/1/summary

### Announcement SSE stream
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/realtime/announcements/1/stream
Accept: text/event-stream